Particle Therapy Project Bergen (PTPB) - tools and models for research in
cancer therapy using photons, protons and heavy ions

Directory layout:
=================

DVHtools/
    This contains scripts used to convert DVH text files to variables stored
    in a Matlab workspace .mat file. Also some utility functions are provided
    to query some basic information about the contents of a DVH file.

Models/
    Contains Matlab scripts that implement functions for the core models.
    These include Organ Equivalent Dose (OED) calculations and slope factor
    calculations.

src/
    Contains code and scripts implementing various general functions for the
    calculation framework.

examples/
    Here you will find some example scripts that should how to use the different
    functions and tools implemented in this code module.

templates/
    This contains some template files to use for code development.
